.DT
when
$MUDNAME$ player help
when

.SH Name
.SI 5
when - Show when someone was last on $MUDNAME$
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
when <player name>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a simple command which shows when someone was last adventuring on 
$MUDNAME$.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> when pilla
Pilla last logged on six days, ten hours, fifty-two minutes and twenty-seven seconds ago.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
whois, finger
.EP
